1. Bundletool Download karo

Bundletool GitHub Releases
 se latest bundletool-all-x.x.x.jar download.

2. Java Install Hona Chahiye

Aapke system me Java 8+ installed hona chahiye.

Check karne ke liye:

java -version

3. .aab se .apks Generate karo

Terminal ya CMD me run karo:

java -jar bundletool-all-1.15.6.jar build-apks --bundle=app-release.aab --output=app.apks --mode=universal

4. .apks ko Extract karo

.apks actually ek ZIP hoti hai. Rename karke unzip karo:

mv app.apks app.zip
unzip app.zip -d output_folder

5. APK Install Karna (Optional)

Direct device me install karne ke liye:

adb install output_folder/universal.apk
